The paper deals with image segmentation using deep learning algorithms, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of ensemble approaches and uncertainty analysis also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves natural language processing techniques such as the Dempster-Shafer theory, which could place it in the information retrieval (cs.IR) or computational linguistics (cs.CL) sub-categories.
